{
  "texts": [
    "Generative AI also carries unique integrity risks.",
    "As mentioned before, its capability to create synthetic data leads to a unique integrity risk-AI hallucination.",
    "In the health care context, generative AI in health care could be used to create fake medical records or alter existing ones.",
    "Fabricated medical data can be fed again into LLMs, further threatening the integrity of medical information.",
    "For instance, the malicious use of deepfakes generated by deep generative models could fabricate a patient's medical history to falsely claim insurance or lead to incorrect treatments."
  ]
}